<title>農桑輯要</title>
<pc>》</pc>之書於民<pc>，</pc>均與王磐所言合<pc>。</pc>惟至元<measure quantity="7" unit="years">
<num value="7">七</num>年</measure>至<measure quantity="10" unit="years">
